---
title: BBQ Spiced Salmon with Green Bean and Apple Salad
description: BBQ spiced salmon tops this summer-inspired delight. Quick roasted green beans get tossed with slivers of crisp apples, toasted almonds and spring mix. A simple oil and vinegar dressing is all you need to bring this whole dish together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saumon-aux-epices-bbq-4af5f0f9.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/bbq-spiced-salmon-606317ed0354f87b116c3bf4-f79695d1.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipes/bbq-spiced-salmon-606317ed0354f87b116c3bf4
